data.title: Siegfried Van Praag
data.text:
Siegfried Van Praag, birth 10 Nov 1889 Amsterdam, died 7 Oct 1931 Amsterdam

Married 26 May 1915 Zaandam, Holland to:

Clara Judith (Juut) Belinfante, birth 22 Apr 1888 Amsterdam, died 7 Oct 1931 Utrecht, Holland, daughter of Abraham (oom Duwkracht) Cohen Belinfante and Rebecca Sequeira
